<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Chhawna</author>
<hymn_number>186</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pielgal gam nuom chu ka tun tiengleh,
 Khawvel beimang ding hi taihsan ing ka;
 Aw, hinlai taksa hi ngai puong ka,
 Hinna thing leh Lalpa chu tung ka.

[V2]
 Tun ka nuom hi, pielgal gam nuom,
 Thokit chate laituol a lennau;
 Thihna, pulthawk, kahna bei tana,
 Aw pielgal kei din hung kihawng in.

[V3]
 2. Gamnuom ka thilin ka lung a hel,
 Belam No leh A tatsate lenna;
 Aw, khawvel ngailo in ei nusieu,
 Zie gam chu ka tung thei tadih puoi.

[V4]
 3. Dan takleh taikhuo hung vak ina,
 Tih ka hetin ka kahlai ka hai sek;
 Lei gimum na ei tuom tehaw hi,
 Pel ingka zie gam chu ka tun tieng.

[V5]
 4. Ziechun ma a thuoka, liem sate,
 Kipakin a leng ui gimthei chate;
 Hukdampa leh a tatsate tawh,
 Kikhen loa I lenna diu chu.</lyrics>
<title>Pielgal Gam Nuom !</title>
</song>